title: Roumanian violin
description:
Collection of old roumanian violin recordings, mostly electrecord. Lost of gypsy musicians. Check out Ion Dragoi for the speed, Mihail Botofei for the poetry and fratii(brothers) Gore for the classic gypsy-style (they are the ones who recorded with Romica Puceano back in th early days...)

Lot's of unidentified stuff too. Help me out ... :-)
